(355, 298, 'char march', 'charlottemarch@btinternet.com', 'http://www.charmarch.co.uk', '86.172.74.34', '2011-01-22 18:11:20', '2011-01-22 18:11:20', 'hey Sally - i love all this stuff - great to see u experimenting so much - ace!  was walking in Ardgour a couple of weeks ago and came across a tiny house with a tiny painted B&amp;B sign perched on top of a frozen waterfall, but didn''t have my camera.  went back a few days later and the ice had thawed so it actually looked a really classy spot for a B&amp;B then!  will try to remember to send u a photo.  keep ''em coming, Sally - it''s great to see u using the environment and its materials so much.  inspiring!', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 7.0; Windows NT 6.0; YPC 3.2.0; SLCC1; .NET CLR 2.0.50727; Media Center PC 5.0; .NET CLR 3.5.30729; .NET CLR 3.0.30729; .NET4.0C; OfficeLiveConnector.1.5; OfficeLivePatch.1.3)', '', 0, 0),
